14:03.995 --> 14:05.618
Now you're ready for action.

14:07.148 --> 14:08.381
Hey, have you talked to Bay?

14:10.516 --> 14:12.730
Oh, right. The T-shirts.

14:15.892 --> 14:17.056
- Hey!
- Hi!

14:17.097 --> 14:18.725
Hey, honey! Mingo.

14:18.760 --> 14:19.735
- Hey.
- Hey.

14:19.794 --> 14:21.559
I'm so glad you guys made it!

14:21.679 --> 14:23.888
Mingo: Lookin' good,
guys. Digging the hats.

14:23.896 --> 14:25.670
I had to wrangle this one.

14:25.682 --> 14:26.929
He claims he has two left feet.

14:26.974 --> 14:28.744
Hey, you'll see. Don't
say I didn't warn you.

14:28.753 --> 14:31.245
Hey, maybe the mechanical
bull is more your speed.

14:32.875 --> 14:34.653
It'd probably be safer.

14:35.134 --> 14:37.069
Nuh-uh. Come on, cowboy.

14:37.070 --> 14:38.558
- Let's break you in.
- (Groans)

14:38.580 --> 14:41.304
- Cool if I put my phone in your jacket?
- Sure.

