29:54.534 --> 29:55.980
This is what's the matter.

29:56.100 --> 29:58.385
You want to tell me how a
receipt got in your pocket

29:58.439 --> 30:01.396
from the auto body shop
where my ex-wife works?

30:01.901 --> 30:03.081
Okay, let me explain.

30:03.118 --> 30:04.614
- You went to Atlanta?
- I should have told you.

30:04.643 --> 30:05.819
I know that.

30:05.856 --> 30:07.293
Does she know who you
are? That we're together?

30:07.331 --> 30:08.963
No. Absolutely not.

30:08.976 --> 30:10.256
- Are you sure?
- Yes.

30:10.293 --> 30:11.943
I was careful. I swear.

30:14.128 --> 30:15.292
So you didn't trust me.

30:15.830 --> 30:17.667
I had to see it for myself...

30:18.344 --> 30:20.314
Before I got more involved with you.

30:22.285 --> 30:23.354
You know what?

30:27.023 --> 30:28.394
I'll find my own way home.

30:30.326 --> 30:32.208
Eric. Eric!

30:39.634 --> 30:41.521
You know, we never really talked

30:41.903 --> 30:43.191
about... him.

30:43.562 --> 30:44.508
Who? Julian?

30:44.865 --> 30:45.771
Yeah, we did.

30:45.829 --> 30:47.550
- I said...
- You said nothing happened,

30:47.612 --> 30:49.212
but the feelings were real...

30:50.142 --> 30:52.336
And we just pushed right past them because

30:52.660 --> 30:53.579
this happened.

30:55.626 --> 30:59.399
Would we still be together
if you hadn't got pregnant?

31:00.284 --> 31:01.722
I hope so.

31:03.155 --> 31:04.746
Do you wish that I was him?

31:05.278 --> 31:07.059
Of course not.

31:12.016 --> 31:13.736
Then what was it about him?

31:17.940 --> 31:21.114
I grew up with double
the expectations on me

31:21.887 --> 31:23.142
because of my brother.

31:23.609 --> 31:24.642
And...

31:25.066 --> 31:28.224
Julian was the kind of guy
that I thought I should be with.

31:29.911 --> 31:32.225
Stable, more money...

31:33.006 --> 31:35.806
Somebody who could give me
the life I thought I wanted.

31:36.471 --> 31:37.568
Stable...

31:38.104 --> 31:39.105
traditional.

31:39.391 --> 31:40.314
Yeah.

31:43.023 --> 31:44.265
And look at you now.

31:44.821 --> 31:46.010
I know.

31:48.589 --> 31:50.168
But I couldn't be happier.

31:50.762 --> 31:51.937
I promise.

31:54.895 --> 31:56.939
I love you, Toby.

31:57.679 --> 32:01.085
And I know we got back
together in an unexpected way,

32:01.276 --> 32:04.147
but the minute we broke
up, I wanted you back.

32:07.226 --> 32:08.185
Me, too.

32:23.532 --> 32:24.768
(Sighs)

32:34.305 --> 32:35.512
(Sighs)

32:38.106 --> 32:39.689
It's not just the shirts.

32:40.682 --> 32:43.171
Hammer girl is officially dead.

32:47.392 --> 32:50.500
But she doesn't belong to me anymore.

32:52.281 --> 32:54.331
She had a great run.

32:54.366 --> 32:57.928
She was our symbol during
the Carlton protest,

32:58.348 --> 33:00.520
I sent her to Afghanistan with Ty.

33:01.035 --> 33:02.405
I leaned on her

33:02.441 --> 33:04.708
a lot over the years, and...

33:07.035 --> 33:10.495
I think now it's time to say goodbye.

33:18.564 --> 33:21.505
It's been four years since I created her,

33:21.535 --> 33:25.448
and I haven't come up with
anything half as good since.

33:30.778 --> 33:34.376
But what if she's the
best thing I'll ever do?

34:03.682 --> 34:04.513
(Scoffs)

34:10.849 --> 34:12.996
You know, I never thought
that you would become

34:13.025 --> 34:16.495
one of my best friends, but you are.

34:27.614 --> 34:28.545
Thank you.

34:37.969 --> 34:39.456
I think I'm gonna stay here,

34:39.731 --> 34:43.237
figure out my next amazing idea.

34:49.686 --> 34:50.780
(Sighs)

35:06.617 --> 35:07.846
Mingo: Whoa!

35:07.888 --> 35:10.256
- That can't all be from the hat.
- Nah.

35:10.281 --> 35:12.184
I gave my speech to the manager.

35:12.346 --> 35:13.837
I was pretty sure

35:13.862 --> 35:16.335
that I could change his mind
if he just gave me a chance.

35:16.372 --> 35:18.902
- And you did!
- No. Not at all,

35:19.056 --> 35:22.009
but the lady who won
the bull riding contest

35:22.043 --> 35:25.297
was sitting nearby and she was quite moved

35:25.324 --> 35:26.791
by what I had to say.

35:26.861 --> 35:31.319
After settling her bar tab, she gave
me what was left of her winnings.

35:31.369 --> 35:32.951
Plus what was in the hat...

35:32.980 --> 35:36.200
Totaled $687!

35:36.495 --> 35:37.817
That's awesome!

35:37.854 --> 35:38.922
Yes!

35:40.432 --> 35:41.971
I couldn't have done it without you.

35:42.391 --> 35:44.756
I can't wait to tell Quinn!

35:47.328 --> 35:49.497
You're still talking with that guy?

35:49.530 --> 35:53.805
Yeah, but just about Pati, the program.

35:53.925 --> 35:55.570
You should have told me.

35:55.753 --> 35:58.114
Told you what? There's nothing going on.

35:58.166 --> 35:59.621
He kissed you.

35:59.783 --> 36:01.382
- But...
- But what?

36:01.449 --> 36:03.771
It's weird that you're talking
with this guy and arranging

36:03.792 --> 36:05.989
this whole fundraiser with
him, and I didn't know about it.

36:08.371 --> 36:09.260
(Sighs)

36:12.156 --> 36:13.303
(Sighs)

36:18.788 --> 36:19.997
(Door opens)

36:23.607 --> 36:24.766
Will's in bed.

36:25.314 --> 36:27.570
I told him you would check
on him when you got home.

36:34.325 --> 36:36.108
Look, are you gonna say anything?

36:38.214 --> 36:39.332
What did you say to her?

36:40.689 --> 36:41.888
What was she like?

36:42.875 --> 36:44.505
She fixed my rental car.

36:44.667 --> 36:45.992
She seemed fine.

36:46.428 --> 36:47.761
Nice even...

36:48.931 --> 36:50.761
Until I realized she was working

36:50.765 --> 36:52.589
with her husband to sell drugs.

36:53.109 --> 36:54.072
Like I told you?

36:54.093 --> 36:55.630
- I know.
- (Sighs)

36:57.284 --> 36:59.623
You told me you were going
to go see your cousins...

36:59.947 --> 37:00.911
In Ohio.

37:01.135 --> 37:02.960
You looked right at me and...

37:02.972 --> 37:04.838
It was a bad lie.

37:04.958 --> 37:06.379
I know that.

37:07.073 --> 37:08.947
But it was important that I know.

37:10.185 --> 37:11.400
- (Sighs)
- Look...

37:11.520 --> 37:13.370
We have got to get past this.

37:13.405 --> 37:14.654
You have to forgive me.

37:14.656 --> 37:16.488
It's not just the lie.

37:17.299 --> 37:18.919
It's that you endangered Will!

37:19.039 --> 37:20.809
But it's been months.

37:21.263 --> 37:22.596
And he's fine.

37:22.974 --> 37:24.702
You're both fine.

37:25.259 --> 37:26.381
Please.

37:30.138 --> 37:31.292
I'm going to bed.

37:40.048 --> 37:42.132
Mingo, wait! Can we talk?

37:42.498 --> 37:43.529
Yeah, we could...

37:43.649 --> 37:45.357
Or you could call Quinn and talk with him

37:45.373 --> 37:47.683
since you seem to be
doing a lot of that lately.

37:48.273 --> 37:51.039
I'm so sorry I didn't tell
you that we'd been talking.

37:53.445 --> 37:54.649
The trip...

37:56.037 --> 37:57.716
Changed something in me...

37:58.000 --> 38:00.901
And he and I have this bond over that.

38:00.903 --> 38:02.370
That you and I don't have.

38:04.039 --> 38:07.273
You and I see each other every day.

38:07.393 --> 38:09.084
We go mountain biking

38:09.138 --> 38:11.289
and drink mint chip shakes at midnight.

38:11.364 --> 38:13.683
But it's not a profound bond about

38:13.757 --> 38:15.324
changing people's lives.

38:16.122 --> 38:16.936
Mingo...

38:16.974 --> 38:18.731
It's cool. I get it.

38:20.526 --> 38:22.229
There is nothing

38:22.437 --> 38:24.691
going on with him. I swear.

38:25.998 --> 38:26.900
Okay.

38:27.810 --> 38:30.530
Do you want to go get mint chip shakes?

38:31.241 --> 38:33.136
I was just about to suggest that.

38:33.198 --> 38:34.718
Let me go grab my wallet.

38:36.804 --> 38:38.521
(Phone vibrates)

38:47.372 --> 38:49.516
(Door opens) Okay.

38:49.636 --> 38:50.717
Let's hit it.

38:57.163 --> 38:58.929
Yeah, it's fine with me.

38:59.511 --> 39:00.629
You made it.

39:00.629 --> 39:02.435
You should have control over it.

39:09.538 --> 39:11.009
I'm fine.

39:12.126 --> 39:14.431
I'm starting a new project, actually.

39:16.775 --> 39:18.088
I don't know yet.

39:18.275 --> 39:20.165
But I think there's something...

39:20.825 --> 39:24.455
something about the
way we define ourselves.

39:34.001 --> 39:35.252
He's good!

39:35.611 --> 39:39.366
Actually, he's been a
really amazing friend lately.

39:39.401 --> 39:41.267
We just... (Sighs)

39:41.303 --> 39:44.024
We have a lot in common.

39:45.131 --> 39:46.439
Anyway...

39:50.145 --> 39:51.867
I should go.

39:51.987 --> 39:55.659
Good luck with the festival and everything.

